What the item is commonly called by others. --&gt;|image         = &lt;!-- An inventory image of the item. --&gt;|release       = &lt;!-- The release date of the item. --&gt;|update        = &lt;!-- A link to the corresponding update page when this item was released, without the Update: prefix. --&gt;|removal       = &lt;!-- The removal date of the item. If the item has not been removed from the game, delete this field. --&gt;|removalupdate = &lt;!-- A link to the corresponding update page when this item was released, without the Update: prefix. If the item has not been removed from the game, delete this field. --&gt;|members       = &lt;!-- If the item is members, Yes or No. --&gt;|quest         = &lt;!-- If the item is a quest item, use [[&lt;Quest Name&gt;]] --&gt;|tradeable     = &lt;!-- If the item is tradeable, Yes or No. --&gt;|equipable     = &lt;!-- If the item is equipable, Yes or No. --&gt;|edible        = &lt;!-- If the item is edible, Yes or No. If it is obviously inedible, for instance a sword, delete this field. --&gt;|stackable     = &lt;!-- If the item is stackable, Yes or No. --&gt;|value         = &lt;!-- Delete this if it has a GEMW value; else use the kept on death interface value. --&gt;|convert       = &lt;!-- Coins you get from choosing &quot;Cash in&quot; on Treasure Hunter. If the item doesn't appear there, delete this. --&gt;|high          = &lt;!-- Coins you get from high-alching the item. If not applicable: No --&gt;|low           = &lt;!-- Coins you get from low-alching the item. If not applicable: No --&gt;|alchable      = &lt;!-- If the item can't be alchemized, delete the above 2 and write No --&gt;|destroy       = &lt;!-- Text when you are trying to destroy the item. If not destructible: Drop --&gt;|death         = &lt;!-- What happens with the item on death. --&gt;|store         = &lt;!-- The prices a store sells the item for when its stock is full. If not sold, use &quot;No&quot; --&gt;|currency      = &lt;!-- If the currency used by the store is other than coins, state the currency. If not, delete this field. --&gt;|seller        = &lt;!-- Store/NPC having a stock of the item. If not sold, delete this field. --&gt;|exchange      = &lt;!-- Use GEMW if its sold on the Grand Exchange. Use No if it is tradeable but not sold. Delete if untradeable. --&gt;|gemwname      = &lt;!-- If the GEMW page here at the wiki uses a different name than the name field, use this to specify that name. --&gt;|examine       = &lt;!-- What the item says when examined. --&gt;|weight        = &lt;!-- The item's weight, not including &quot;kg&quot; or other suffixes --&gt;}}

{{Infobox Item| name       = &lt;!-- The item's real name, not a short form. --&gt;| AKA        = &lt;!-- What the item is commonly called by others. --&gt;| image      = &lt;!-- An image of the item. --&gt;| members    = &lt;!-- If the item is members, Yes or No. --&gt;| quest      = &lt;!-- If the item is a quest item, Yes or No. If yes, state the name of the quest. --&gt;| tradable   = &lt;!-- If the item is tradable, Yes or No. --&gt;| equipable  = &lt;!-- If the item is equipable, Yes or No. --&gt;| stackable  = &lt;!-- If the item is stackable, Yes or No. --&gt;| high       = &lt;!-- Coins you get from high-alcing the item.  If not applicable: No --&gt;| low        = &lt;!-- Coins you get from low-alching the item.  If not applicable: No --&gt;| destroy    = &lt;!-- Text when you are trying to destroy the item.  If not destructible: Drop --&gt;| store      = &lt;!-- The prices the general/speciality store SELLS the item for when its Main Stock is full. --&gt;| currency   = &lt;!-- If the currency used is other than coins, state the currency. If not applicable: No --&gt;| low        = &lt;!-- Coins you get from low-alching the item.  If not applicable: No --&gt;| destroy    = &lt;!-- Text when you are trying to destroy the item.  If not destructible: Drop --&gt;| store      = &lt;!-- The prices the general/speciality store SELLS the item for when its Main Stock is full. --&gt;| currency   = &lt;!-- If the currency used is other than coins, state the currency. {{Infobox Item| name       = &lt;!-- The item's full name, exactly as it appears in-game. --&gt;| AKA        = &lt;!-- What the item is commonly called by others. --&gt;| image      = &lt;!-- An image of the item. --&gt;| release    = &lt;!-- Release date of the item, in DD Month YYYY format. --&gt;| update     = &lt;!-- The title of the update with which it was released. --&gt;| members    = &lt;!-- If the item is members, Yes or No. --&gt;| quest      = &lt;!-- If the item is a quest item, Yes or No. If yes, state the name of the quest. --&gt;| tradeable  = &lt;!-- If the item is tradeable, Yes or No. --&gt;| equipable  = &lt;!-- If the item is equipable, Yes or No. --&gt;| edible     = &lt;!-- If the item is edible, Yes or No. Delete this field if it is something obviously inedible, like a sword. --&gt;| stackable  = &lt;!-- If the item is stackable, Yes or No. --&gt;| high       = &lt;!-- Coins you get from high-alcing the item. Use &quot;No&quot; if it cannot be alchemised --&gt;| low        = &lt;!-- Coins you get from low-alching the item. Use &quot;No&quot; if it cannot be alchemised --&gt;| destroy    = &lt;!-- Text displayed when you try to destroy the item.  If not destructible use &quot;Drop&quot;. --&gt;| store      = &lt;!-- The price that a specialty store SELLS the item for when its Main Stock is full. Use &quot;No&quot; if no store stocks this item. Do not use General store prices for this field. --&gt;| currency   = &lt;!-- If the currency used is other than coins, state the currency.  Otherwise, delete this field. --&gt;| seller     = &lt;!-- Store/NPC which stocks this item. --&gt;| exchange   = &lt;!-- Use &quot;gemw&quot; if the item is sold on the Grand Exchange. Delete this field if it is untradeable. Use &quot;No&quot; if it is tradeable, but not sold on the Grand Exchange --&gt;| examine    = &lt;!-- What the item says when examined. --&gt;| weight     = &lt;!-- The item's weight. Use just a number, do not include &quot;kg&quot;. --&gt;}}

Do not include the prefix &quot;Update:&quot;. --&gt;|members    = &lt;!-- If the item is members, Yes or No. --&gt;|quest      = &lt;!-- If the item is a quest item, Yes or No. If yes, state the name of the quest. --&gt;|tradeable  = &lt;!-- If the item is tradeable, Yes or No. --&gt;|equipable  = &lt;!-- If the item is equipable, Yes or No. --&gt;|edible     = &lt;!-- If the item is edible, Yes or No. Delete this field if it is something obviously inedible, like a sword. --&gt;|stackable  = &lt;!-- If the item is stackable, Yes or No. --&gt;|high       = &lt;!-- Coins you get from high-alcing the item. Use &quot;No&quot; if it cannot be alchemised. --&gt;|low        = &lt;!-- Coins you get from low-alching the item. Use &quot;No&quot; if it cannot be alchemised. --&gt;|destroy    = &lt;!-- Text displayed when you try to destroy the item. If not destructible use &quot;Drop&quot;. --&gt;|store      = &lt;!-- The price that a speciality store SELLS the item for when its Main Stock is full. Use &quot;No&quot; if no store stocks this item. Do not use General store prices for this field. --&gt;|currency   = &lt;!-- If the currency used is other than coins, state the currency. Delete this field if it is untradeable. Use &quot;No&quot; if it is tradeable, but not sold on the Grand Exchange --&gt;|examine    = &lt;!-- What the item says when examined. --&gt;|weight     = &lt;!-- The item's weight.
